{"ja315:0.1":"Jataka ","ja315:0.2":"Catukkanipata ","ja315:0.3":"Pucimandavagga ","ja315:0.4":"5. Sabbamamsalabhajataka ","ja315:1.1":"“Pharusa vata te vaca, ","ja315:1.2":"mamsam yacanako asi; ","ja315:1.3":"Kilomasadisi vaca, ","ja315:1.4":"kilomam samma dammi te”. ","ja315:2.1":"“Angametam manussanam, ","ja315:2.2":"bhata loke pavuccati; ","ja315:2.3":"Angassa sadisi vaca, ","ja315:2.4":"angam samma dadami te”. ","ja315:3.1":"“Tatati putto vadamano, ","ja315:3.2":"kampeti hadayam pitu; ","ja315:3.3":"Hadayassa sadisi vaca, ","ja315:3.4":"hadayam samma dammi te”. ","ja315:4.1":"“Yassa game sakha natthi, ","ja315:4.2":"yatharannam tatheva tam; ","ja315:4.3":"Sabbassa sadisi vaca, ","ja315:4.4":"sabbam samma dadami te”ti. ","ja315:5.1":"Sabbamamsalabhajatakam pancamam. "}